column5: i would just like to say hi to everyone on this website as i am a new member.  i was previously a member on the old website but took a little beak over the winter and then came on the other day and realized the format of the site had changed.  i look forward to contributing lots of pictures and hope to see many as well.
Welcome back Jamie, it hasn't been the same without you... literally! Some nice changes and more user features. Look forward to your reports. -Brian
Lotsa Pictures - Hear that Roy - Lotsa Pictures!!  Welcome aboard! Take yer shoes off, an come back, ya hear!
Welcome back.  I see you puit up a nice Walleye pic as well.    Looking forward to others.
Its Ok to have a little beak Jamie.....I just wouldnt mention it here!!!!!!!!  Might bring a few giggles out of the younger folk!
